    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254670/extras/ff06325fbbb8fb80e0d38cd88c925f7e.avif?t=1770472761\" width=620 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You arrived to help your uncle with crops in the fields. But of a sudden, you've been attacked by a tractor monster. To rescue the village, you must collect crops and defeat Teddy the tractor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254670/extras/fdb1568905df9e9bccb28092ec49e9ea.poster.avif?t=1770472761\" width=620 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254670/extras/fdb1568905df9e9bccb28092ec49e9ea.webm?t=1770472761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254670/extras/fdb1568905df9e9bccb28092ec49e9ea.mp4?t=1770472761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of the most important parts of Teddy the Tractor is the tractor. You will ride your tractor, upgrade it, unlock new weapons, and fight Teddy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the gameplay, you move through the story by committing quests and collecting crops day by day. Time moves forward constantly, and some quests can be missed or failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you will </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight various tractorheads</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect corn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your tractor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to villagers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Teddy the Tractor </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
